cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper is about improving the quality of conversational responses generated by neural models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also uses adversarial training and optimization techniques, which are common in the fields of machine learning and artificial intelligence, hence cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on improving diversity and informativeness, which are related to the concepts of novelty and creativity, respectively. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Sound) are also possible categories, as they deal with these topics.
